        <summary lang="en_GB">Radio Deejay</summary>
        <description lang="en_GB">Kodi, like a deejay. Access reloaded and webradios content from deejay.it from your media player of choice. Radio DeeJay is an Italian radio station. It was founded on 1 February 1982 by the Italian radio and television personality Claudio Cecchetto and was acquired by the Gruppo Editoriale L'Espresso in 1989 (which also owns DeeJay TV, Repubblica Radio TV, m2o and Radio Capital).</description>
        <disclaimer lang="en_GB">Unofficial, I'm just a fan.</disclaimer>
        <summary lang="it">Deejay RELOADED</summary>
        <description lang="it">Kodi, like a Deejay. Accedi ai reloaded e alle webradio di deejay.it dal tuo riproduttore multimediale preferito.
        </description>
        <disclaimer lang="it">Non ufficiale, sono solo un fan.</disclaimer>
